des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : support@geosmartpro.com

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off the fan.
There’s no need to go to the fan to turn it on/off - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your GeoSmartPro products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our “GeoSmartPro” app on your Android or iOS app store;
(2). Register an account in our “GeoSmartPro” app;
(3). You need to have your GeoSmartPro smart products nearby;
(4). Configure these devices in our GeoSmartPro app and set the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in the “GeoSmartPro” skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure your Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search “GeoSmartPro” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of “GeoSmartPro”, and you'll be navigated to the GeoSmartPro login page;
(9). Input your GeoSmartPro account username and password, you'll be redirected to the success page;
(10). You have now completed the setup. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your AirGo Smart Fan or AirLit ring light:
- Turn On/Off
“Alexa, turn on the Bedroom Fan”
“Alexa, turn off the Bedroom Fan”.
- Turn On/Off
“Alexa, turn on the Bedroom Light”
“Alexa, turn off the Bedroom Light”. 
-Speed Control: 
“Alexa, change AirGo speed to 1"
“Alexa, change AirGo speed to 2"
“Alexa, change AirGo speed to 3"
